body:
Necklace: stacking damage;
Q: cleave and piercing attack;
W: empowered can clear CC and makes you immune for next one;
E: same;
R: crits.

I never liked Rengar but this is too much.  He will cc you, crits you, cleave you and your friends, pierce your armor, and there is nothing you can do about it, because he&#039;ll 2 of your ccs! Isn&#039;t Azir and Ekko had to teach Riots why overloaded kits are bad design? Damn, I never liked new Fiora&#039;s mechanics for stopping cc. And now we&#039;ll have another even more broken thing.

